# GSD Web — environment variables
#
# ─── Local mode (default) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# No variables required. The app spawns a local `gsd --mode rpc` child per
# project and uses the local #token fragment auth flow.
#
# GSD_WEB_AUTH_TOKEN   optional bearer token required on every /api/* request
# GSD_WEB_PROJECT_CWD  optional default project path

# ─── Cloud mode (ADR-047) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Set GSD_CLOUD_MODE=1 to run inside the gsd-cloud SaaS. ALL THREE gateway
# variables are then required — the server refuses to boot without them.
#
# GSD_CLOUD_MODE=1
#
# Internal base URL of the cloud gateway (server-to-server, not public):
# GATEWAY_INTERNAL_URL=http://gateway.internal:9100
#
# Shared secret authenticating /internal/rpc/token and /internal/fs calls:
# GATEWAY_INTERNAL_TOKEN=change-me
#
# HMAC secret for app bridge tokens (bootstrap) and 8h session cookies:
# APP_BRIDGE_SECRET=change-me
